1. BAC to strictly comply with the posting and submission requirements of the GPPB to provide full information and transparency to the public;
2. Sangguniang Bayan to henceforth pass an ordinance on the creation of a special account in the general fund (SAGF) for the BGCM to facilitate the monitoring of the fund’s utilization;
3. Supply and/or Property Officer and Inspecting Officer to fill out the date and other necessary details in the Purchase Order and Acceptance and Inspection Report to assure that the items received are in accordance with the contract; and
